#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga"
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Bhikkhusutta"
msgstr "7. A Mendicant"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.257"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.7:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihariṃsu, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā "
"bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the mendicants in the past …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissanti, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā "
"bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "future …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"viharanti, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""
"present who realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life, and who live having realized it with their own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements, do so by developing and cultivating the four "
"bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.7:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "higher mind …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.6"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihariṃsu sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā "
"bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "All the mendicants in the past …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.7"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ "
"bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "future …"

msgctxt "sn51.7:2.8"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi bhikkhū āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"viharanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā "
"bahulīkatattā”ti."
msgstr ""
"present who realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life, and who live having realized it with their own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements, do so by developing and cultivating these four "
"bases of psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.7:2.9"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
